            <p class="sec-body-sm p-break">I'm dedicated to producing a user-centric designs that satisfies the <b>users</b> and builds trust between the brand and the users. For this reason, I build my designs to be intuitive, and easy to use. I'm open to receive feedbacks that will make me <b>grow</b> and develop my skills.</p>
            <p class="sec-body-sm p-break"> I came from Seoul to Vancouver in 2003. It's been a long journey and therefore, I look for trust and stability in my relationships and what I do. I'm very fortunate to have great <b>friends</b> and <b>community</b> who helped me to be who I am today. And I seek to implement what I value in my design.</p>
            <p class="sec-body-sm p-break">Outside of work, I like to hand wash my car or go out for a photoshoot with a nice walk.</p>
